{{Quote|An AT3 Directive is not debatable.|[[Sate Pestage/Legends|Sate Pestage]]|<ref name="X-Wing Rogue Squadron 30">[[X-Wing Rogue Squadron 30|''X-Wing Rogue Squadron'' 30]]</ref>}}
An '''AT3 Directive''' was an [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] directive that ordered all members of the [[Imperial Military/Legends|Imperial Military]] and intelligence agencies to give full cooperation and support to the code's user. The Directive is specifically used at the full discretion and authority of the Director of [[Imperial Intelligence/Legends|Imperial Intelligence]], alongside those who hold the office of [[Grand Moff/Legends|Grand Moff]].

